-- ESTRPIPE is Linux-specific (hardware suspend from ALSA); it is not present on FreeBSD.
-- The ALSA compatibility library on FreeBSD never returns this errno, so defining it as
-- an out-of-range sentinel makes the match arms unreachable without compile errors.
--- src/host/alsa/mod.rs.orig
